    <p><b>Bake element failure</b>, 8-12 year typical. $240-$420.</p>
    <p><b>Convection fan motor wear</b>, $320-$520.</p>
    <p><b>Control board lockout</b>, factory reset resolves some; replacement $420-$720.</p>
